TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Thats why we gave you lead napkins

 

Waiter theres a dog in my soup!

If it’s the red tomato soup then you ordered the Clifford big red dog special.

Waiter! There’s a panzerkamfwagen V in my soup!

You lost "p". You loose.

Waiter! A plate of alphabet soup for that mister.

Waiter: It is Alphabet soup, it is just the cuneiform alphabet.

Customer: Waiter There is an image of me looking down on an image of me, looking down on an image of me......... in my soup.

It's a mirror plate. Put it back on the wall.

Waiter! You brought this food only because you want my money.

I do not get any of this money, only tips. Here let me get you a drink and a straw with that sir.

 

Waiter! There's a leftist with a rightist fetish in my soup!

What a sidistic soup.

3 minutes ago, Dientus said:

I do not get any of this money, only tips. Here let me get you a drink and a straw with that sir.

Okay, then that's a tip for you. I don't eat the straw, I'm not a cow.

Waiter! See above.

A leftist with a rightest fetish?

Waiter! Theres a food im my soup.

Apologies sir, it was meant to be in the soup and not im.

 

Waiter there's a spare letter M in my soup!

yes, and it eats your soup.

Waiter, theres water in my soup.

Waiter: Yes that is to  stop it drying out.

Customer:Waiter, there is a Donald in my soup.

Yes, it's a duck soup. Would you prefer Uncle Scrooge instead?

Waiter! A glass of boiling water and a straw.

Waiter: Yes sir, one grass tea soup coming up.

Customer: Waiter, there is an enigma in my soup.

Time to start crackin' the code!

 

 

Waiter! There's a miniature SCP-914 in my soup!

Put in your spoon, get the crackers out the other side.

 

Waiter! There is a chunk of metal in my soup!

Well then why did you come to the heavy metal themed restaurant?

Waiter! There’s a clock in my soup!

Waiter: The Chef needed more Thyme.

Customer: Waiter there is no time in my soup.

FINISH IT FAST!

 

 

Waiter, there's a straight line in my soup

It's just an uncooked noodle.

 

Waiter! There are noodles in my soup!

Ah yes you ordered the noodle soup. What did you expect?

Waiter! There’s a blender in my soup!

Or is the soup in the blender?

Waiter, there's a fly in my soup!

Ah, yes, we catch them so.

Waiter! Where can I select a proper fly in this menu?

[bot--0047]: ERROR: Unrecognized; Request does not match "waiter theres (userprompt) in my soup" format

Waiter, there's @Souptime in my soup!

Edited November 15, 2023 by iamn00b
haha sploosh

Because Souptime did not start the next joke, let me just do it...

 

 

Waiter! There are the Americas in my soup! And there's a tiny ship with a tiny Kristopher Kerman on it about to find them and think he's in India
